Package com.cyberfront.crdt

The com.cyberfront.crdt package includes the core classes to build and manage a commutative CRDT for managing JSON document updates using the JSON Patch standard. The final result of the CRDT is a JSON document. In some case, certain operations on the document may not be consistent with the document, and those operations are ignored when encountered.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCRDT
    This is an abstract base class for CRDT classes.
    CRDTManager
    The CRDTManager class is used to wrap a CRDT instance so as to interact with it.
    GenericCRDTManager<T>
    The Class GenericCRDTManager is used to manage a Plain Old Java Object (POJO).
    LastWriteWins
    The LastWriteWins class implements a Last Write Wins commutative CRDT.
    LastWriteWins.TrialResult
    The Class TrialResult is used to process a collection of operations provided to it.
    OperationTwoSet
    This is an abstract class which defines a Two Set CRDT.
